{"tid":1076752,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［隻狼］","createTime":"2019-03-25T05:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T05:50:01.000Z","uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2015a02e6d57d049f6b516aa402016c95df8d12","tid":1076752,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"月光大劍是From Software的&ldquo;祖傳&rdquo;武器，但由於和&ldquo;隻狼：影逝二度&rdquo;的世界觀設定不合，開發者們並沒在遊戲中加入這把武器。近日MOD製作者TKGP分享了一款由他製作的&ldquo;隻狼&rdquo;月光大劍MOD，能讓你在葦名城用上月光大劍。<br />\n<br />\nTKGP將遊戲中狼的佩刀模型替換成了月光大劍，這位製作者還為玩家們提供了兩種不同的&ldquo;月光大劍&rdquo;：其一是&ldquo;黑暗之魂3&rdquo;中的月光大劍，另一款是&ldquo;血源詛咒&rdquo;中的聖潔月光劍，各位玩家可以根據自己的喜好選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gw3N8cR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgw3N8cR.png&h=e8f4bef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMod下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nexusmods.com/sekiro/mods/5?tab=description\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fsekiro%2Fmods%2F5%3Ftab%3Ddescription&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6fMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=514ca4f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nexusmods.com/sekiro/mods/5?tab=description</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}